    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси фуқароларини Тошкент шаҳри ва Тошкент вилоятида доимий яшаш ва вақтинча турган жойи бўйича рўйхатга олиш тартиби тўғрисида</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;\">ИЛТИМОСНОМА</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Фуқаро </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;\">{#6}Номзоднинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> Ўзбекистон Республикаси </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;\">{#7}Номзод ишлаётган давлат органи ёки ташкилотнинг номи</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">га </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;\">{#8}Номзоднинг лавозими</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> лавозимига ишга қабул қилинганлиги (тайинланганлиги) сабабли «Тошкент шаҳри ва Тошкент вилоятида яшаш жойи бўйича доимий рўйхатга олиниши лозим бўлган Ўзбекистон Республикаси фуқаролари тоифаларининг Рўйхати тўғрисида»ги Ўзбекистон Республикаси Қонуни билан тасдиқланган Рўйхатнинг 11-бандига мувофиқ ушбу фуқаро </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;\">{#9}Прописка қилинадиган ҳудуд</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">да доимий яшаш жойи бўйича рўйхатга олинишини сўраймиз.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Фуқаро </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;\">{#6}Номзоднинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> ишончлилигига кафолат берамиз.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Илова: </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;\">{#10}Илтимосномага илова қилинаётган ҳужжатлар номи</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;\">{#2}Илтимоснома киритаётган давлат органи ёки ташкилотнинг мансабдор шахсининг мансаби</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;\">{#3}Мансабдор шахс Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;\">{#4}Илтимоснома киритилган сана</span></p>\n</div></div>",
